# Telegram Desktop Installation  
(Debian trixie + XFCE + Korean Desktop Folder)

This document explains how to install **Telegram Desktop** on  
**Debian trixie (testing)** where `telegram-desktop` is not available via `apt`,  
using **Flatpak**, and how to create a **desktop launcher on an XFCE system**
with a **Korean desktop folder (`바탕화면`)**.

---

## 1. System Environment

- OS: Debian trixie (testing)
- Desktop Environment: XFCE
- Home directory language: Korean (`~/바탕화면`)
- Installation method: Flatpak (recommended)

---

## 2. Install Flatpak

```bash
sudo apt update
sudo apt install flatpak
Add the Flathub repository (required once):

bash
코드 복사
sudo flatpak remote-add --if-not-exists flathub https://flathub.org/repo/flathub.flatpakrepo
3. Install Telegram Desktop (Flatpak)
bash
코드 복사
flatpak install flathub org.telegram.desktop
Test run:

bash
코드 복사
flatpak run org.telegram.desktop
4. Verify the Telegram Launcher File
Check the Flatpak application launcher location:

bash
코드 복사
ls /var/lib/flatpak/exports/share/applications | grep telegram
Expected output:

코드 복사
org.telegram.desktop.desktop
5. Create a Telegram Desktop Icon (XFCE – Korean Desktop)
5.1 Copy the launcher to the Desktop folder
bash
코드 복사
cp /var/lib/flatpak/exports/share/applications/org.telegram.desktop.desktop ~/바탕화면/
5.2 Rename the launcher (optional)
bash
코드 복사
mv ~/바탕화면/org.telegram.desktop.desktop ~/바탕화면/Telegram.desktop
5.3 Grant execute permission (required)
bash
코드 복사
chmod +x ~/바탕화면/Telegram.desktop
6. Allow Execution in XFCE (Important)
Right-click the Telegram icon on the desktop

Select Properties

Enable “Allow this file to run as a program”

Close the dialog

Or mark the launcher as trusted via terminal:

bash
코드 복사
gio set ~/바탕화면/Telegram.desktop metadata::trusted true
7. Launch Test
Double-click the Telegram desktop icon

Telegram Desktop should start successfully

8. Notes
On Debian trixie, telegram-desktop may not be available in APT repositories

Flatpak is the most reliable installation method in this environment

Flatpak launcher path:

swift
코드 복사
/var/lib/flatpak/exports/share/applications/
On XFCE with a Korean desktop directory,
execute permission and launcher trust must be set manually

9. Useful Commands Summary
bash
코드 복사
flatpak run org.telegram.desktop
chmod +x ~/바탕화면/Telegram.desktop
gio set ~/바탕화면/Telegram.desktop metadata::trusted true
